thread.title: Chinese space station will crash, but it probably won't hit you

title: Chinese space station will crash, but it probably won't hit you
text:
Chinese space station will crash, but it probably won't hit you   01:34 
China's first space station, the Tiangong-1, is expected to fall to Earth this weekend in a fiery blaze of glory. Scientists say they don't know where it will land, but there's a less than one in a million chance it will hit anyone. Matthew Larotonda reports.
